snippet.title: Trepang2 Bladekisser DLC Announcement Trailer
snippet.description:
Trepang2 Bladekisser DLC is out July 25 on Steam, Xbox Series X|S and PlayStation 5!

It’s time to get up close and personal 💞

DLC Content:
👊 2 new missions: TF63 command center and Omega Facility
💥 9 combat simulator maps
⚔️ 3 new weapons: sword, revolver, machine gun
 ❗   3 high-value targets
📝 10 new intel documents

Are you worthy enough to wield the blade?

Trailer Music: @wearedarknet &  https://www.instagram.com/dal_av/

Thank you @noodle5021 for helping with additional footage.

Steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/1164940/Trepang2/
Twitter: https://twitter.com/TrepangStudios
Discord: https://trepang2.com/discord

#TrepangStudios #Trepang2 #wkdisgood
